I can't sleep at night.

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:03.080
I'm afraid of relapsing.

00:02:03.590 --> 00:02:05.040
It was so hard to get clean.

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:06.770
You can't throw it all away now.

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:10.520
I know.

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:13.500
As long as I don't see it again,

00:02:14.030 --> 00:02:15.630
I can definitely keep going.

00:02:16.400 --> 00:02:17.840
Even if you don't think about yourself,

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:19.470
you should think about Cotton.

00:02:19.470 --> 00:02:21.800
It wasn't easy
to get the life you have now.

00:02:27.630 --> 00:02:29.160
Cotton has suffered enough

00:02:29.400 --> 00:02:30.280
living with me.

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:34.650
Did something happen to you recently?

00:02:36.590 --> 00:02:37.079
No,

00:02:37.630 --> 00:02:39.280
just complaining.

00:02:42.590 --> 00:02:43.390
Your glasses.

00:02:44.630 --> 00:02:45.240
Thank you.

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:46.930
If you encounter any difficulties in life,

00:02:46.930 --> 00:02:48.240
[Nanzhou Limin Road Police Station]

00:02:48.240 --> 00:02:49.170
call me anytime.

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:53.079
[Police Office]

00:02:53.079 --> 00:02:53.870
Bye-bye, Cotton.

00:02:53.870 --> 00:02:54.630
Say goodbye to me.

00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:55.160
Bye-bye.

00:02:55.750 --> 00:02:56.280
Bye-bye.

