[Police Office]

00:03:36.230 --> 00:03:39.410
[No Parking in the Emergency Exit Passage]

00:03:49.470 --> 00:03:50.240
You've been following me all the way.

00:03:50.240 --> 00:03:51.170
What do you want?

00:03:58.280 --> 00:03:59.210
It's me, Yipeng.

00:04:06.400 --> 00:04:09.000
I really do have
something to discuss with you.

00:04:14.750 --> 00:04:18.760
♪ Hoping you'll turn back
and meet me again in fragrant blooms ♪

00:04:19.860 --> 00:04:23.440
♪ Eembrace the endless void ♪

00:04:23.990 --> 00:04:24.560
[Fook Convenience Store]

00:04:24.560 --> 00:04:26.620
♪ It will mock me with a smile ♪

00:04:27.460 --> 00:04:32.409
♪ Blind to consequence,
heedlessly indulging my whims ♪

00:04:32.409 --> 00:04:37.140
[High-quality and Convenient]

00:04:37.310 --> 00:04:38.970
Since I've already bought it.

00:04:46.390 --> 00:04:47.590
My mom is at home.

00:04:47.930 --> 00:04:50.330
It's not convenient to bring you upstairs.

00:04:50.440 --> 00:04:51.040
It's fine.

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.680
How's your mother?

00:04:53.380 --> 00:04:54.840
Just tell me what you want.

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:56.170
No need to be polite.

00:05:02.740 --> 00:05:03.310
It's hot.

00:05:04.390 --> 00:05:07.790
Drinking and eating hot things
can cause esophageal cancer.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:09.460
What about you?

00:05:10.300 --> 00:05:10.330
Do you have disappearing cancer

00:05:10.330 --> 00:05:11.270
[High-quality and Convenient]

00:05:11.270 --> 00:05:12.930
or irresponsibility cancer?

00:05:15.070 --> 00:05:15.970
You're right about everything.

00:05:15.970 --> 00:05:17.430
I have all kinds of cancer.

00:05:25.790 --> 00:05:27.120
Why are you coming to me?

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.310
I'm investigating a case.

00:05:30.310 --> 00:05:31.340
I need your help.

00:05:33.390 --> 00:05:35.120
So you only come to me for a case.

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:36.850
That's fine.

00:05:37.460 --> 00:05:39.860
At least
it lets me know you're still alive.

00:05:44.650 --> 00:05:45.360
Go ahead.

00:05:45.630 --> 00:05:46.230
What is it?

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:51.240
A woman came to you
right before you got off work today.

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:52.700
She works at a music store.

00:05:53.180 --> 00:05:54.340
Are you close to her?

00:05:55.390 --> 00:05:56.409
You mean Zhan Cui?

00:05:58.480 --> 00:05:59.080
I think so.

00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:01.890
When she was in rehab,

00:06:02.070 --> 00:06:04.140
Lin Qiong and I
were responsible for her case.

00:06:04.140 --> 00:06:05.800
After I was transferred
to the police station,

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:07.660
I found out she lives in this area.

00:06:08.190 --> 00:06:10.070
No wonder
I felt something was off about her.

00:06:10.070 --> 00:06:12.090
She has a history of drug use.

00:06:12.960 --> 00:06:14.090
What are you saying?

00:06:14.190 --> 00:06:15.790
She's been clean for 2 years.

00:06:15.870 --> 00:06:17.400
Then why did she come to you?

00:06:18.120 --> 00:06:19.720
She said she wasn't feeling well

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:21.320
and was afraid of relapsing.

00:06:23.310 --> 00:06:25.190
This doesn't have
anything to do with you, does it?

00:06:25.190 --> 00:06:26.120
I don't know her.

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:28.040
However,

00:06:28.040 --> 00:06:29.560
I suspect she's connected to

00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:32.020
a drug trafficking case I'm investigating.

00:06:32.220 --> 00:06:33.350
That's impossible.

00:06:34.310 --> 00:06:37.350
She wouldn't touch drugs again
for her daughter's sake.

00:06:37.350 --> 00:06:39.120
When I went to the music store today,

00:06:39.120 --> 00:06:41.980
I could tell she had relapsed
just by looking at her.

00:06:42.270 --> 00:06:44.600
Isn't she looking for you as a substitute?

00:06:44.900 --> 00:06:47.430
I can tell her condition
with just one glance.

00:06:47.630 --> 00:06:48.520
Yang Yipeng,

00:06:48.830 --> 00:06:49.830
don't be so judgmental.

00:06:49.830 --> 00:06:50.870
I'm not being judgmental.

00:06:50.870 --> 00:06:52.240
Whether she uses or not
doesn't matter to me.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:53.270
I don't care about that.

00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:55.070
What I actually care about is...

00:06:58.270 --> 00:06:58.720
Right.

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:02.100
You only care about your case.

00:07:05.270 --> 00:07:06.400
I care about people.

00:07:10.310 --> 00:07:11.640
I deserve to be scolded,

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:14.410
and you're
the most qualified person to do it.

00:07:14.410 --> 00:07:16.350
But could you not scold me right now?

00:07:16.350 --> 00:07:18.310
I told you I'm investigating a case.

00:07:18.310 --> 00:07:19.440
I now suspect

00:07:19.830 --> 00:07:20.600
there's a drug-dealing point

00:07:20.600 --> 00:07:22.130
hidden in that music store.

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:25.330
It's Baiye Music Store.

00:07:27.390 --> 00:07:28.340
Who's the owner?

00:07:29.890 --> 00:07:31.350
The owner is called Bai Di.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:33.480
I met him during my previous visits.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:35.930
He and Zhan Cui knew each other before.

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:39.020
But Zhan Cui cares
deeply about her daughter.

00:07:39.020 --> 00:07:42.240
She wouldn't get involved in
drug trafficking for her daughter's sake.

00:07:42.240 --> 00:07:44.360
And the fact that she came to
the police station to find me today

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:46.690
shows she's resistant to the whole thing.

00:07:47.070 --> 00:07:47.870
I understand.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:49.330
Thank you

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:51.490
for sharing this information with me.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:52.980
Then I'll...

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:56.340
I'll get going.

00:07:59.270 --> 00:08:00.270
Stop right there.

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:12.850
You're just leaving like this?

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:15.040
In my current state,

00:08:15.040 --> 00:08:16.500
I shouldn't be around you.

00:08:18.390 --> 00:08:21.320
Won't you even ask
how I've been these past few years?

00:08:25.750 --> 00:08:27.350
Yongwei, I'm in a lot of debt.

00:08:27.850 --> 00:08:28.660
A lot.

00:08:29.630 --> 00:08:30.710
I owe Captain Wu.

00:08:30.950 --> 00:08:31.880
I owe my parents.

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:33.470
And I owe you most of all.

00:08:33.919 --> 00:08:35.650
Just give me a little more time.

00:08:36.470 --> 00:08:38.330
I'll pay back each debt one by one.

00:08:38.909 --> 00:08:39.440
Pay back?

00:08:41.030 --> 00:08:43.159
How are you going to pay anything back?

00:08:43.409 --> 00:08:46.070
You didn't even
come back when your father died.

00:08:49.590 --> 00:08:51.320
Look at the state you're in now.

00:08:55.150 --> 00:08:55.950
Is it worth it?

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:00.240
I'm sorry.

00:09:47.840 --> 00:09:48.550
Bye-bye.

00:09:48.580 --> 00:09:49.600
Come on, say goodbye to your teacher.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:50.600
Bye-bye.

00:09:51.700 --> 00:09:53.870
School's out. Take your time going home.

00:09:53.870 --> 00:09:55.240
How was it, Cotton?

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:57.480
Did your teachers praise you today?

00:09:57.790 --> 00:09:58.460
Yes!

00:09:58.500 --> 00:09:59.720
Cotton is the best!

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:01.600
[Dadi Kindergarten]

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:03.600
What nice songs did you learn today?

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:04.630
Will you sing them
for mommy when we get home?

00:10:04.630 --> 00:10:05.180
Zhan Cui.

00:10:08.070 --> 00:10:09.530
Let's find a place to talk.

00:10:11.550 --> 00:10:13.210
What's your daughter's name?

00:10:13.890 --> 00:10:14.780
Cotton.

00:10:17.840 --> 00:10:18.580
As for me,

00:10:18.670 --> 00:10:20.630
I'm Officer Luo from the police station.

00:10:20.630 --> 00:10:21.890
I'm coming to you today

00:10:22.380 --> 00:10:24.180
to learn about some situations.

00:10:25.570 --> 00:10:26.630
What's this about?

00:10:27.030 --> 00:10:28.870
I wanted to talk to you last night.

00:10:28.870 --> 00:10:31.000
In our station, we have all the records

00:10:31.030 --> 00:10:32.740
of the drug offenders.

00:10:33.150 --> 00:10:34.030
Recent reports show

00:10:34.030 --> 00:10:36.030
your behavior's been a bit unusual.

00:10:36.550 --> 00:10:37.490
Officer Luo,

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:39.470
I've been staying off drugs.

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:41.890
I'm clean now.

00:10:44.630 --> 00:10:45.670
Clean?

00:10:47.640 --> 00:10:48.720
Let me tell you,

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:51.080
you may fool Officer Ruan,

00:10:51.080 --> 00:10:52.280
but you can't fool me.

00:10:56.200 --> 00:10:57.930
When did you start using again?

00:11:02.610 --> 00:11:04.410
I'm meeting you privately today

00:11:04.790 --> 00:11:07.190
because I don't want
to make this a big deal.

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.080
If this is your attitude,

00:11:10.080 --> 00:11:10.980
then I have no choice.

00:11:10.980 --> 00:11:12.150
We'll bring Cotton along

00:11:12.150 --> 00:11:14.280
and go to the station for questioning.

00:11:14.480 --> 00:11:14.960
Okay?

00:11:15.190 --> 00:11:15.920
Hey, Cotton.

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:17.080
I'm sorry.

00:11:17.960 --> 00:11:18.960
I'm really sorry.

00:11:22.070 --> 00:11:23.840
The one you should be sorry to is not me,

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:25.280
but yourself.

00:11:27.270 --> 00:11:28.480
I took it by accident.

00:11:29.390 --> 00:11:30.480
I really didn't know

00:11:30.480 --> 00:11:31.270
that record

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:34.090
had LSD stamps in it.

00:11:36.390 --> 00:11:37.120
What record?

00:12:16.250 --> 00:12:18.380
I've been clean for several years now.

00:12:18.720 --> 00:12:20.780
I failed to control myself this time.

00:12:21.450 --> 00:12:22.470
It was my mistake.

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:24.760
I promise

00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:26.930
I'll never touch those things again.

00:12:27.150 --> 00:12:29.350
I'll report to Officer Ruan every week.

00:12:30.410 --> 00:12:31.080
Please,

00:12:31.790 --> 00:12:33.120
give me one more chance.

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:35.100
I can give you a chance,

00:12:35.480 --> 00:12:37.140
but you need to tell the truth.

00:12:37.600 --> 00:12:38.200
I promise.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:42.180
Is your record store dealing LSD stamps?

00:12:44.840 --> 00:12:45.300
Well...

00:12:45.500 --> 00:12:47.360
I don't know anything about that.

00:12:47.900 --> 00:12:49.680
I'm giving you a chance right now.

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:50.680
Understand that.

00:12:51.120 --> 00:12:52.030
I really don't know.

00:12:52.030 --> 00:12:53.320
I'll ask you one more time.

00:12:53.320 --> 00:12:54.790
Is your record store

00:12:55.550 --> 00:12:58.000
dealing LSD stamps?

00:12:58.200 --> 00:13:00.200
Think carefully before you answer.

00:13:03.410 --> 00:13:04.810
Look at Cotton.

00:13:05.120 --> 00:13:06.200
So cute.

00:13:07.550 --> 00:13:08.390
Such an adorable child...

00:13:08.390 --> 00:13:09.120
Officer Luo.

00:13:09.930 --> 00:13:10.970
You can't do this.

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:12.330
What am I supposed to do?

00:13:13.550 --> 00:13:15.350
You won't even tell me the truth.

00:13:15.670 --> 00:13:17.070
Let me tell you, Zhan Cui,

00:13:17.550 --> 00:13:18.870
I can forgive your relapse.

00:13:18.870 --> 00:13:20.630
But if you're

00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:23.700
involved in drug trafficking...

00:13:26.550 --> 00:13:27.820
Nobody can help you.

00:13:28.130 --> 00:13:28.760
Nobody.

00:13:29.390 --> 00:13:30.120
Officer Luo,

00:13:30.840 --> 00:13:32.420
I swear on my life

00:13:32.680 --> 00:13:34.000
and my daughter's

00:13:34.550 --> 00:13:36.240
that I have nothing to do with this...

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:37.920
If you're not involved, prove it.

00:13:37.920 --> 00:13:38.920
Tell me the truth.

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:56.000
At night, the boss

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:58.260
usually doesn't let me stay in the store.

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:00.030
Especially on Tuesdays,

00:14:00.030 --> 00:14:01.800
he makes me leave early.

00:14:02.670 --> 00:14:04.000
But he stays at the store

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:05.630
to receive deliveries.

00:14:05.630 --> 00:14:07.690
Isn't receiving deliveries normal?

00:14:07.790 --> 00:14:09.850
But one day I accidentally saw

00:14:10.080 --> 00:14:11.080
that the delivery

00:14:11.150 --> 00:14:12.150
was baby formula.

00:14:14.240 --> 00:14:15.170
A record store

00:14:15.240 --> 00:14:16.570
stocking baby formula?

00:14:17.150 --> 00:14:17.600
Why?

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:19.130
Doesn't that seem strange?

00:14:22.080 --> 00:14:23.080
I didn't dare ask,

00:14:23.600 --> 00:14:25.000
and I didn't want to know.

00:14:25.270 --> 00:14:26.930
This has nothing to do with me.

00:14:28.960 --> 00:14:31.960
I just want a job
where I'm not discriminated against.

00:14:32.320 --> 00:14:33.920
I have a child to take care of.

00:14:36.550 --> 00:14:38.680
What's your relationship with Bai Di?

00:14:40.790 --> 00:14:41.960
We met in a band before.

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:42.600
Friends?

00:14:44.350 --> 00:14:45.010
Not really.

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:46.550
What about the deliveries?

00:14:46.550 --> 00:14:48.080
Where might they be stored?

00:14:49.040 --> 00:14:50.900
There's a warehouse in the store,

00:14:50.990 --> 00:14:52.250
but I've been in there,

00:14:52.480 --> 00:14:53.550
and there are only instruments,

00:14:53.550 --> 00:14:54.480
no baby formula.

00:14:55.080 --> 00:14:55.960
So where do you think

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:57.690
the baby formula might be kept?

00:14:59.490 --> 00:15:00.460
I don't know.

00:15:01.000 --> 00:15:02.480
All the receiving and shipping

00:15:02.480 --> 00:15:04.320
is handled by him
and a few of his friends.

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.520
I never get involved.

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:09.390
And usually,

00:15:09.410 --> 00:15:10.480
he doesn't allow me

00:15:10.670 --> 00:15:11.640
into his office.

00:15:12.960 --> 00:15:14.080
Think carefully again.

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:16.480
Is there anything else
you haven't told me?

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:18.570
Mom.

00:15:19.130 --> 00:15:20.460
Cotton.

00:15:21.080 --> 00:15:21.600
What's wrong?

00:15:21.600 --> 00:15:22.960
Bad man!

00:15:23.090 --> 00:15:26.230
Don't be mean to my mom!

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:27.400
Cotton.

00:15:27.430 --> 00:15:28.200
You can't talk like that.

00:15:28.200 --> 00:15:29.120
I didn't.

00:15:29.140 --> 00:15:30.670
I was just talking with your mom.

00:15:30.670 --> 00:15:31.390
Don't worry.

00:15:31.390 --> 00:15:32.710
He's a good man.

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:33.460
Go play now.

00:15:33.670 --> 00:15:34.290
Go play.

00:15:39.080 --> 00:15:40.680
Have you thought it through?

00:15:41.390 --> 00:15:42.990
There's nothing more to say?

00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:43.940
Officer Luo,

00:15:44.390 --> 00:15:46.210
that's all I know.

00:15:46.940 --> 00:15:48.400
I've told you everything.

00:15:49.390 --> 00:15:50.840
Don't tell anyone

00:15:50.840 --> 00:15:51.870
about what we discussed today.

00:15:51.870 --> 00:15:52.780
Promise me.

00:15:55.490 --> 00:15:57.150
Don't touch that stuff again.

00:15:59.000 --> 00:15:59.480
Don't.

00:16:15.810 --> 00:16:16.710
Officer Luo!

00:16:20.630 --> 00:16:22.360
If Bai Di is trafficking drugs,

00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:24.260
will he be sentenced to death?

00:16:24.920 --> 00:16:26.120
Do you want him to die?

00:16:26.620 --> 00:16:28.350
He should get what he deserves.

00:16:33.570 --> 00:16:33.800
Overdosing on drugs

00:16:33.800 --> 00:16:35.480
[Case Information]

00:16:35.480 --> 00:16:37.480
and accidentally falling to death.

00:16:37.670 --> 00:16:39.950
Completely consistent
with the forensic report.

00:16:39.950 --> 00:16:42.130
So it has nothing to do with Mai Jiamin.

00:16:42.690 --> 00:16:43.890
She's been released.

00:16:44.450 --> 00:16:44.910
Zhi'an.

00:16:45.620 --> 00:16:46.400
We have work to do.

00:16:46.400 --> 00:16:46.870
Coming.

00:16:50.530 --> 00:16:51.840
This is the record
where drugs were hidden.

00:16:51.840 --> 00:16:53.080
See if you can find out

00:16:53.080 --> 00:16:54.680
where this record came from.

00:17:01.660 --> 00:17:01.790
